    v2 = v0
    tmp = (((v1 + 0.75 / tmp + 0.31) * (v1 + 0.36 - tmp + 0.52)) + 0.27)
    v0 = (tmp / (v2 / (tmp + 0.62 + tmp + 0.73)))
    v1 = v1
    tmp = wp.cos(0.92)
    v0 = (wp.abs(0.99) + wp.exp((v2 + 0.11 + v0 + 0.48)))
    tmp = 0.10
    v1 = ((v0 - wp.abs(v0 + 0.23)) / v2)
    data[tid] = v0
